致平衡唔到。"},{"pid":"43d92aa2695ef405b282a67e9781cea764a01cd8","tid":1072591,"uid":235623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"創意係無限"},{"pid":"3adba3a71f478d7d49ee74361f01dcdeb2d9edb3","tid":1072591,"uid":33904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"78ec090814e1d6072423b8db47ffd9c9fe9ff1cf","tid":1072591,"uid":33904,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"261f6cafcd8b362f8d67f7fb24f6feb5fca0ca93","tid":1072591,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"音符真係得咁多<br />\n全世界有咁多億人<br />\n 可能係世界第二邊有條友同你首曲作得好類似都唔奇<br />\n填詞唔同 有成二千幾個中文字 難d撞到<br />\n咁如果咁啱得咁橋 真係同人好類似<br />\n咁又點洗脫抄歌嫌疑呢<ins></ins>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:53:58.000Z","msg":"作曲=將自己聽過既音樂消化完再嘔返出黎，<br />\n愈清楚自己係獨一無二既歌=愈抄得多人。<br />\n<br />\n作一首歌抄一兩首就叫做抄，<br />\n作一首歌抄十首歌唔叫抄。<br />\n<br />\n例如我verse用A歌既chord progression，<br />\n編曲用B歌既編法，音色、樂器構成又跟C歌，呢一段野出黎已經係變左獨一無二，<br />\n然後一首歌又有n個部分，<br />\nintro, verse, prechorus, chorus, solo, outtro，每個部分都mix &amp; match下，根本唔會係自己作完抄左人都唔知，每個作曲、編曲既人心裡其實都好清楚邊部分係學左d咩人，知道自己作既野係集n人之大成就唔會怕比人話係抄。個d比人話抄既，一係就功力唔夠，取材不足，一係就係太想重現個首歌既感覺，導致平衡唔到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:21:15.000Z","msg":"用一個人盡可夫既Chord progression黎講下所謂既作曲同抄襲，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jEy6MGu3bIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjEy6MGu3bIA&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=81b2705b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jEy6MGu3bIA</a><br />\n有個鬼佬作既經典歌：Just the two of us<br />\n<br />\nChord progression 係IV maj7 -&gt; III7-&gt; vi min7 -&gt; I7 (4361)<br />\n簡單四個chord有7度音、有out key notes (來自於唔係diatonic既III7, I7) 製造tension，又有得無限loop。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Twfe0owTVVI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTwfe0owTVVI&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=12bf2408\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Twfe0owTVVI</a><br />\n最近另一個唔出名鬼佬作既歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i9I55MZLYYY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi9I55MZLYYY&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=ded5f52e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i9I55MZLYYY</a><br />\n椎名林檎學完之後：丸の内サデスティック，原編曲版已經搵唔到，得東京事變編曲版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P8xXD9Pi1OU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP8xXD9Pi1OU&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=48f66b5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P8xXD9Pi1OU</a><br />\n某香港band<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3LVAmMxICoA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3LVAmMxICoA&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=d9680e71\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3LVAmMxICoA</a><br />\n椎名林檎用4361配bossa nova，作左長く短い祭り<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CuILryzL4g8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCuILryzL4g8&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f5a1443f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CuILryzL4g8</a><br />\n同人夾東京事變用rock玩4361， 空が鳴っている<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4JkIs37a2JE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4JkIs37a2JE&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=a881530b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4JkIs37a2JE</a><br />\nJamiroquai用4361改出黎既名曲 virtual insanity<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NyddMMiViZc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyddMMiViZc&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=04192a8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NyddMMiViZc</a><br />\n日本仔用virtual insanity chord progression作出黎既歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tvUMCOWrTgA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtvUMCOWrTgA&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=7e17ddff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tvUMCOWrTgA</a><br />\nOOHYO - Pizza<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9qRCARM_LfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9qRCARM_LfE&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=2ffb3279\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9qRCARM_LfE</a><br />\nあいみょん - 愛を伝えたいだとか<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5eIhj6CJoWs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5eIhj6CJoWs&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=293ca216\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5eIhj6CJoWs</a><br />\nSuper girls - 鎂光燈下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BiBTpQPCMtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBiBTpQPCMtg&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=16c8929d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BiBTpQPCMtg</a><br />\nLUCKY TAPES - レイディ・ブルース<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rm5PZuWmM4o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Frm5PZuWmM4o&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=4cc30d75\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rm5PZuWmM4o</a><br />\nメランコリック写楽 「成仏できない」<br />\n<br />\n呢度有幾多稱得上抄，有幾稱得上作，自己感受下，每個人睇法都唔同，我覺得真係抄既實際上唔多，好多都有加其他元素落去，但有少部分連用同一首歌兩個元素或以上，成件事就會變到好抄。好多時B學完A加上好多其他元素製造出自己既音樂，然後C又學B再學埋B既「其他元素」，結果就會變抄。<br />\n<br />\n我仲其實仲有好多好多例子，多到講唔哂。"},{"pid":"ee5679177f8cbc6ba936de28cbb573284c82a6ab","tid":1072591,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78ec090814e1d6072423b8db47ffd9c9fe9ff1cf","tid":1072591,"uid":33904,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"261f6cafcd8b362f8d67f7fb24f6feb5fca0ca93","tid":1072591,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"音符真係得咁多<br />\n全世界有咁多億人<br />\n 可能係世界第二邊有條友同你首曲作得好類似都唔奇<br />\n填詞唔同 有成二千幾個中文字 難d撞到<br />\n咁如果咁啱得咁橋 真係同人好類似<br />\n咁又點洗脫抄歌嫌疑呢<ins></ins>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:53:58.000Z","msg":"作曲=將自己聽過既音樂消化完再嘔返出黎，<br />\n愈清楚自己係獨一無二既歌=愈抄得多人。<br />\n<br />\n作一首歌抄一兩首就叫做抄，<br />\n作一首歌抄十首歌唔叫抄。<br />\n<br />\n例如